body:
### Welcome...

...to my GitHub page. Not much to see here just yet, but thanks for stopping by. I have a few things here on GitHub (@clayford) if you want to poke around. Most of it is materials for workshops that I have taught for the [StatLab](http://data.library.virginia.edu/statlab/) at the University of Virginia.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
